 DevOps End-to-End CI/CD Project with Jenkins, Docker & Kubernetes

This project demonstrates a complete **CI/CD pipeline** using Jenkins, Docker, DockerHub, and Kubernetes deployed on AWS EC2 instances.

---

## 📌 Project Architecture

GitHub → Jenkins → Docker Build → DockerHub → Kubernetes Deployment → Application Live

---

## 🧰 Technologies Used

- Linux (Ubuntu)
- Jenkins (CI/CD Automation)
- Docker (Containerization)
- DockerHub (Image Registry)
- Kubernetes (k3s) for orchestration
- AWS EC2 (Cloud Infrastructure)
- Git & GitHub (Version Control)

---

## 🚀 Features

- Automated CI/CD pipeline using Jenkins
- Docker image build and push to DockerHub
- Kubernetes deployment using YAML manifests
- Exposed application using NodePort service
- Scalable deployment with replicas

