## ⚙️ CI/CD Pipeline Steps

1. Developer pushes code to GitHub
2. Jenkins detects changes
3. Jenkins builds Docker image
4. Image pushed to DockerHub
5. Kubernetes pulls image
6. Application deployed on EC2 cluster

